title: The Invisible Mr. Unmei (1951) SEEDY TOKYO NOIR

sources.title: The Invisible Mr. Unmei (1951) SEEDY TOKYO NOIR
sources.description:
1st Time on YouTube! Exclusive FRIDAY at PizzaFLIX edition
Directors: George Breakston, C. Ray Stahl
Stars: Byron Michie, Martha Hyer, Tetsu Nakamura

Get lost in the seedy Tokyo underworld of Post War Japan with cinema guilty pleasure MARTHA HYER as an American who travels to Orient to uncover the truth behind her brother’s untimely death. Also known as Oriental Evil.

TRIVIA: UNMEI means “fate” in Japanese. According to legend,  Mr. Unmei is an invisible supernatural entity that only appears to evil men and knows the secret passions hidden in their minds.
